  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Cook chicken breast in a skillet with 1 tbsp olive oil until browned and cooked through.",
    "In a separate bowl, mix together creamy sauce and brazilian spice blend.",
    "In a greased 9x13 inch casserole dish, arrange cooked chicken, then pour creamy sauce mixture over the top.",
    "Sprinkle shredded cheddar cheese evenly over the top.",
    "Drizzle remaining 1 tbsp olive oil over the cheese.",
    "Bake for 25-30 minutes, or until cheese is melted and bubbly.",
    "Garnish with sliced scallions before serving."
